# Skills Bridge

This project uses the Agent Skills open standard (SKILL.md format) as the
single source of truth for all AI behavioral rules.

All rules live in `.skills/*/SKILL.md`. Read and follow them.

Key skills to always observe:
- `.skills/vibe-scope-control/SKILL.md` — no silent scope expansion
- `.skills/vibe-no-any/SKILL.md` — any is forbidden
- `.skills/vibe-spec-first/SKILL.md` — no spec, no code
- `.skills/vibe-contracts/SKILL.md` — runtime contracts at all I/O
- `.skills/vibe-fault-isolation/SKILL.md` — section crashes must be contained
- `.skills/vibe-state-management/SKILL.md` — no boolean soup

For the full development workflow: `.skills/vibe-develop/SKILL.md`
For running guards: `.skills/vibe-guard/SKILL.md`
For generating pages: `.skills/vibe-gen-page/SKILL.md`
